{"tid":1200054,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間智慧]嘉頓雜餅會唔會係最好既裝備？","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:02:23.000Z","uid":15716,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59882e1c0f416956e7f846111214d31020885b87","tid":1200054,"uid":15716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"雖然嘉頓紅罐雜餅係連登仔最撚憎收到既新年食品，但就係呢一張圖啟發到我<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwVjWs6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwVjWs6.png&h=cc53e2fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉頓雜餅除左有食唔哂既餅乾用黎補充體力之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢個罐仲有好多用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，例如當做容器裝物資裝水，又可以套係手作為防具。有音樂細胞既又可以用個罐黎做戰鼓振奮士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就咁拎住敲擊都已經可以製造到聲音維持大家既士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘉頓雜餅仲唔係去野餐最好既裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e4f99fa7c4e491fbb14b27dc34cbc9dc29adfa","tid":1200054,"uid":257849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"【大整合】11/6-12/6 資訊整合 「反送中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199978</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n整合曬資料 唔該大家入黎集中推！"}]}